  "title": "[ NO EXP ] Sales Engineer ( Industrial Division - Precision Tool ( Weighting Machine ) UP 4K #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Engineer (Industrial Division)</strong></p><p><strong>Sector:</strong> Industrial / Engineering Sales<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Permanent</p><p>This role focuses on business development and solution selling within the industrial sector. You will work with customers to understand their needs, present technical solutions, and grow long-term partnerships.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prospect and generate new business leads</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with customers</li><li>Conduct product demonstrations, seminars, and technical presentations</li><li>Prepare sales proposals and negotiate contracts</li><li>Achieve monthly and annual sales targets</li><li>Meet weekly sales activity targets</li><li>Collaborate with marketing on sales strategies and campaigns</li><li>Monitor industry trends and provide market feedback</li><li>Participate in trade shows and industry events</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Business, Sales, Marketing, Engineering, or related field</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please click “ APPLY NOW”<br /><br />Or you may send in your resume to:<br />Whatsapp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/+6597430026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://wa.me/+6597430026</a>  <br />Email : <a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br /><br />Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
